    About The Store

    LIQUOR WORLD , incorporated in 2013, one of the biggest (online/offline) Wholesale/Retail Liquor Store in Kathmandu, Nepal offers widest selection of genuine domestic and foreign wine, whisky, beer, bourbon, scotch, tequila, vodka, rum, liqueur, beverages, cigarettes, mixers and other spirits at best price. We provide Free Delivery inside ringroad of Kathmandu with purchase of Rs. 1500 and above, Outside Ringroad (Extra Delivery Charge) will be added. Our delivery hours are from 11AM to 8PM and we are 365 days open at your service.
